lead_paragraph: Bernd Wiesberger of Austria shot his second straight 5-under 66 to take the lead Friday in the KLM Open, one shot ahead of playing partner Joost Luiten, who was one of three players tied for second.

headline.print_headline: Wiesberger Takes 1-Stroke Lead After 2nd Round of KLM Open
